<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.212405>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Siconema diducuncinum sp. n. A & B, female & male in copula; C – H, female; I, J, male. C: pharynx region; C: posterior region; D: hooks; and G, I: hooks into D, G, I: hooks; J: posterior region. Except I, all in lateral position. Scale bars in µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/212405/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.212406>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Siconema diducuncinum sp. n. SEM images. Female. A: hooks, dorsal view; B: stomatal tube, en face view; C: caudal organ, dorsal view; D: caudal organ, lateral view; E: margin of sub-lateral field. Scale bars in µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/212406/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

